# Security headers for all static asset responses.
# Workers Static Assets serves files directly at the edge without invoking the
# Worker, so these header-only protections must live here rather than in code.
# (The Content-Security-Policy is delivered via a <meta> tag in index.html.)
/*
  X-Frame-Options: SAMEORIGIN
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
